title: Instagram is the best way to market to teens, says Piper Jaffray survey
text: Teens "overwhelmingly prefer" when brands advertise on Instagram rather than other social media channels, a Piper Jaffray survey finds.

title: The UK is going after Big Tech over harmful content: Here's why it matters
text: Britain just announced plans for a tough new law aimed at forcing tech giants like Facebook and Twitter to clean up their platforms.

title: Facebook says has made headway against abuses ahead of India election
text: Facebook officials touted new fact-checking efforts and technological advances such as the ability to detect when videos had been doctored.

title: The Wall Street Journal: Facebook wants to build underwater cable dubbed ‘Simba’ around Africa
text: Facebook is in talks to develop an underwater data cable that would encircle the continent.
